<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei Light";font-size:20.0pt'
lang=3Den-GB>心室中膈缺損（Ventricular Septal Defect）</p>

</div>

<div style=3D'direction:ltr;margin-top:.0388in;margin-left:.3368in;width:1.5444in'>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.0pt;color:#666666'
lang=3Den-GB>13 April 2025</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.0pt;color:#666666'
lang=3Den-GB>18:17</p>

</div>

<div style=3D'direction:ltr;margin-top:.3965in;margin-left:0in;width:7.9409in'>

<ul style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in'>
 <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#244061'
      lang=3Den-GB><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt'>定義</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>心室中隔缺陷，導致左心室和右心室之間有病理性交通</span></li>
  </ul>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#C00000'
       lang=3Den-GB><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;
       color:black'>導致血液從壓力較高的左心室流向壓力較低的右心室，形成</span><span style=3D'font-family:
       "Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>左至右分流</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>
       (left-to-right shunting)</span></li>
  </ul>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#244061'
      lang=3Den-GB><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt'>流行病學</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#C00000'
       lang=3Den-GB><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>最常見的先天性心臟病，佔</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'> 25%</span></li>
  </ul>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>單獨發生（沒有合併其他心臟缺損）的發生率為</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'> 0.3%</span></li>
  </ul>
 </ul>
 <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#1F3763'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt'>病因</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#1F3763'>大多為先天性，但</span><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;
       color:#F79646'>少見會有後天造成</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
       font-size:11.0pt;color:#1F3763'>，</span><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;
       font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#F79646'>心肌梗塞後或主動脈瓣置換術後</span></li>
  </ul>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#366092'><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>危險因子</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt'>三染色體症</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt'>：</span><span style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:
        11.0pt;color:#C00000'>Down syndrome</span><span style=3D'font-family:
        "Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>（</span><span style=3D'font-weight:
        bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt;color:#F79646'>VSD</span><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt;color:#F79646'>為唐氏症最常合併的先天性心臟病</span><span style=3D'font-family:
        "Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）、</span><span style=3D'font-family:
        Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Edward syndrome</span><span style=3D'font-family:
        "Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>、</span><span style=3D'font-family:
        Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Patau syndrome</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt'>懷孕時期感染</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt'>：</span><span style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:
        11.0pt;color:#C00000'>TORCH</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt'>母體因素</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt'>：</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>糖尿病、肥胖、抽菸</span></li>
   </ul>
  </ul>
 </ul>
 <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
  margin-bottom:0in'>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#244061'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt'>分型</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
       style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>自行癒合機率</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>：</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>M&gt;P&gt;A&gt;S</span></li>
  </ul>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#366092'
       lang=3Den-GB><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>膜型</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0pt'> (Perimembranous type)</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:black'
        lang=3Den-GB><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt;color:#C00000'>最常需要手術介入，</span><span style=3D'font-family:Calibri;
        font-size:11.0pt;color:black'>80%</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt;color:black'>的病例需要手術介入</span></li>
   </ul>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#131314'>位於</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>室間隔的膜部</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#131314'>，其邊緣可能包括三尖瓣環、肌性間隔，以及可能的主動脈環</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#131314'>缺損可能較大，常伴隨非冠狀動脈瓣（</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt;color:#131314'>noncoronary</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#131314'>）或右冠狀（</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt;color:#131314'>right
        coronary</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt;color:#131314'>）主動脈瓣葉脫垂，進一步造成主動脈瓣閉鎖不全。</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>不過在幼兒時期發現的小型缺損，通常會於成長過程中逐漸自行閉合</span></li>
   </ul>
  </ul>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#366092'
       lang=3Den-GB><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>肌肉型（</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0pt'>Muscular type</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>）</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>最常見的類型</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>，</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>但最常自行癒合</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>可能出現在心臟的前部（</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>anterior</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）、中部（</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>midventricular</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）、後部（</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>posterior</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）、心尖部（</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>apical</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>）</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>發生在心室中隔的肌肉部</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>，完全被心肌組織包圍</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>可以是</span><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt;color:#F79646'>單一或多個開口</span></li>
    <ul type=3Dsquare style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
     margin-bottom:0in'>
     <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
         style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt;
         color:#F79646'>“Swiss-cheese” type</span><span style=3D'font-family:
         "Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>：</span><span style=3D'font-family:
         "Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>罕見</span><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>，</span><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>心室中膈上有多個小孔</span><span
         style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>，導致左右心室間有多個通道，手術修補難度增加</span></li>
    </ul>
   </ul>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#366092'
       lang=3Den-GB><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>動脈下型（</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0pt'>Subarterial type</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt'>）</span></li>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#C00000'
        lang=3Den-GB><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt;color:black'>發生在</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>主動脈瓣、肺動脈瓣或兩者附近</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#C00000'
        lang=3Den-GB><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt;color:#C00000'>常伴隨主動脈瓣葉脫垂</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt;color:black'>，特別是</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>右冠狀動脈瓣（</span><span style=3D'font-family:
        Calibri;font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>right coronary cusp</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>）</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:black'>，導致</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>主動脈瓣逆流</span></li>
   </ul>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
        style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt;color:#F79646'>東方人較西方人常見</span></li>
   </ul>
   <ul type=3Dcircle style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#C00000'
        lang=3Den-GB><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt'>最難自行癒合，需手術</span></li>
   </ul>
  </ul>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt;color:#366092'>入口型</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0pt;color:#366092'>/</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:14.0pt;color:#366092'>房室管型（</span><span
       style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0pt;color:#366092'>Atrioventricular
       canal type</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
       font-size:14.0pt;color:#366092'>）</span><span style=3D'font-family:Calibri;
       font-size:14.0pt;color:#366092'> </span></li>
   <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#C00000'
        lang=3Den-GB><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:
        11.0pt;color:#131314'>位於</span><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
        font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>三尖瓣下方</span></li>
   </ul>
   <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
    margin-bottom:0in'>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>常合併</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>房室瓣（</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>AV valve</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'>）脫垂、逆流</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt'>常合併</span><span
        style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt;color:#C00000'> Down
        syndrome</span></li>
    <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle' lang=3Den-GB><span
        style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;color:#F79646'>很少自行癒合，需手術</span></li>
   </ul>
  </ul>
  <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#244061'><span
      style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:16.0pt'>病生理</span></li>
  <ul type=3Ddisc style=3D'direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
   margin-bottom:0in'>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#C00000'
       lang=3Den-GB><span style=3D'font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";font-size:11.0pt;
       color:black'>可能發展成</span><span style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:
       11.0pt;color:black'> </span><span style=3D'font-family:Calibri;font-size:
       11.0pt;color:#C00000'>Eissenmenger’ syndrome</span></li>
   <li style=3D'margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#C00000'
       lang=3Den-GB><span style=3D'font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei";
       font-size:11.0pt;color:black'>心室中隔缺損</span><span style=3D'font-weight:
